VM 生成确认
Check Script
	Win - PS1
	Linux - sh
		scp -rp 10.68.41.122:/tmp/linux_check_250916.sh /tmp/linux_check_250916.sh
		scp -rp 10.68.38.122:/tmp/linux_check_250916.sh /tmp/linux_check_250916.sh
		sed -i 's/\r$//' linux_check_250916.sh

必要的确认工作
Account 设置
win - AD 向负责人请求生成
Linux - VM 生成时请VM负责人一同请求
Disk 확인
볼륨 사이즈/타입/마운트 포인트/fstab 등 
Permission(User Account)
Chrony 설정 확인
DL - Corp AD.
WX - Branch AD.
DNS 확인
Agent 설치
OBM
Ontune
SSR
Maxgauge (DB서버의 경우)
L4 DSR Setting

작업 명령

Linux APP Account 추가
groupadd -g 1002 app  
useradd -g 1002 -u 1002 -s /bin/bash app

groupadd -g 1002 app  
useradd -g 1002 -u 1002 -s /bin/bash app



Data Disk 추가
fdisk -l |grep "/dev/sd"
fdisk /dev/sdb
  n > p > 1 > Enter > Enter > t > 8e(Linux LVM) > w
pvcreate /dev/sdb1
vgcreate vg_data /dev/sdb1
lvcreate -l +100%FREE -n lv_data vg_data

mkfs.xfs /dev/mapper/vg_data-lv_data
mkdir /data1
chown -R app:app /data1

mount -a

vi /etc/fstab
/dev/mapper/vg_data-lv_data /data1 xfs defaults 0 0


Chrony 확인 및 변경
chronyc sources
vi /etc/chrony.conf
  server 10.68.56.21 iburst
  server 10.68.56.22 iburst
systemctl restart chronyd.service
systemctl status chronyd.service


